<b>1. </b> Generate words for the following features:<br/>
<b>English</b>:<br/>
<table>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> boy</td>	<td><b>category:</b> noun</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> child</td>	<td><b>category:</b> noun</td>		<td><b>number:</b> plural</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> play</td>	<td><b>category:</b> verb</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> male</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td>	<td><b>person:</b>first</td>		<td><b>tense:</b> simple-present</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> play</td>	<td><b>category:</b> verb</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> male</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td>	<td><b>person:</b> third</td>		<td><b>tense:</b> simple-present</td></tr></table>
<br/>
<b>Hindi</b>:<br/>
<table>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> पुस्तक(pustak)</td>	<td><b>category:</b> noun</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> female</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td>	<td><b>case:</b> direct</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> बाग(bAg)</td>	<td><b>category:</b> noun</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> male</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td>	<td><b>case:</b> oblique</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> खेल(khel)</td>	<td><b>category:</b> verb</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> female</td>		<td><b>number:</b> plural</td>		<td><b>person:</b> third</td>		<td><b>tense:</b> present-perfect</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>root:</b> पढ़(paD)</td>		<td><b>category:</b> verb</td>		<td><b>gender:</b> female</td>		<td><b>number:</b> singular</td>	<td><b>person:</b> first</td>		<td><b>tense:</b> simple-future</td></tr></table>
