	    <b><u>STEP1: </u></b>Select the language.<br>
<b><u>OUTPUT: </u></b>Drop downs for selecting root and other features will appear. <br><br>
<b><u>STEP2: </u></b>Select the root and other features.<br>
<b><u>STEP3: </u></b>After selecting all the features, select the word corresponding above features selected.<br>
<b><u>STEP4: </u></b>Click the check button to see whether right word is selected or not<br>
<br>
<b><u>OUTPUT: </u></b>Output tells whether the word selected is right or wrong
